:INFO
How a Simple Kratky Setup Works
The Kratky method requires no pump, no electricity for water movement, and no \
timer beyond what controls your lights. Plants sit in net pots above a reservoir \
of nutrient solution. Roots hang down and drink as the water level drops, \
creating an air gap that delivers oxygen directly to the root zone. Top off \
with fresh nutrient solution as levels fall. It is the lowest-friction way to \
get started with hydroponics before committing to a more complex recirculating system.

