:INFO
Mix Your Nutrient Solution
Use a two or three part hydroponic nutrient concentrate formulated for leafy greens. \
Follow label ratios: typically 5 ml of each part per gallon of water. Check EC \
(electrical conductivity) with a cheap pen meter: target 1.2 to 1.8 mS/cm for seedlings,

:PATH
Start Seeds or Transplant Cuttings
Soak rockwool cubes or coco coir plugs in pH 5.5 water before seeding.
|
:INFO
Start Seeds or Transplant Cuttings
Soak rockwool cubes or coco coir plugs in pH 5.5 water before seeding. Plant one to two \
seeds per plug, cover lightly, and keep moist and warm (70 to 75 F). Germination for \
basil takes 3 to 5 days. Once roots poke out of the plug, transfer to a net pot

