:INFO
Manage Light and Airflow
Leafy herbs need 14 to 16 hours of light per day under grow lights or a bright \
south-facing window in summer. LED grow panels at 2 to 4 inches above canopy work well \
for compact setups. Add a small USB fan on low to create gentle stem movement: this

:QUOTE
Hydroponics rewards attention to numbers. pH off by half a point and basil \
will yellow within a week. Get it right and the same plant doubles in two weeks.

